<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Welcome to Our App</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        background-color: #007bff;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #555;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Our App, <%= @user.first_name %>!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>
        <p>
          Thank you for signing up! We're excited to have you on board. Below are your account details:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @user.email %></li>
          <li><strong>Sign-up Date:</strong> <%= @user.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To get started, visit our website and log in to explore all the features waiting for you!
        </p>
        <p>
          If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email or reach out to our support team.
        </p>
        <p>
          Cheers,<br>
          The Team
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>
          &copy; <%= Time.now.year %> Our App. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
